The Czech Republic is also

13
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:26,200
the most successful post-communist country

14
00:00:26,200 --> 00:00:27,580
in central Europe.

15
00:00:27,880 --> 00:00:29,980
Unlike some other post-Soviet nations,

16
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:30,990
the Czech Republic—

17
00:00:30,990 --> 00:00:31,990
